Software: Training and testing with ORL face database by Neural Network
Author: Hy Truong Son
Major: BSc. Computer Science
Class: 2013 - 2016
Institution: Eotvos Lorand University
Email: sonpascal93@gmail.com
Website: http://people.inf.elte.hu/hytruongson/
Final update: October 4th, 2015
Copyright 2015 (c) Hy Truong Son. All rights reserved. Only use for academic purposes.

Accuracy
--------
Training: 320 samples
Testing: 80 samples
Accuracy: > 95%

Note
----
Users can reorder the file all-samples.dat to change the training and testing sets. Training set contains the first 80% of samples.

Structure
---------
~/MyLib/: Contains library
~/ORL_Face_Database/: Contains the ORL database
Training_Testing.java: Run both training and testing
training.java: Training separately
testing.java: Testing separately
weights.dat: Contains the weights of the trained neural network
